
= UpgradeDemocracy.org

=Description=

"Upgrade Democracy is a coalition of teams and organizations working on tech-based solutions to systemic problems in governance / group decision-making. Its primary goal is to enhance collaboration and knowledge sharing between its member organizations, and it will be co-facilitated by those orgs. They will convene at the Upgrade Democracy Summit, possibly compete for the Upgrade Democracy Challenge, and collaborate on the Upgrade Democracy Wiki knowledgebase. UpgradeDemocracy.org will serve as a portal for these projects/resources, as well as a launchpad for people to get involved in the movement to upgrade democracy. (It is currently a staging site for The [[Dynamic Democracy Initiative]].)"
(http://upgradedemocracy.org/about/)


